InlayHints:
  Designators: No
  Enabled: Yes
  ParameterNames: No
  DeducedTypes: No

CompileFlags:
  Add: [
    -std=c++17,
    -Werror=shadow
  ]
  Compiler: clang++

Diagnostics:
  ClangTidy:
    Add: [ cppcoreguidelines*, performance*, bugprone*, clang-analyzer*, darwin*, abseil* ]
    Remove: [
      modernize-use-trailing-return-type,
      cppcoreguidelines-avoid-magic-numbers,
      cppcoreguidelines-special-member-functions,
    ]